{"tid":1887642,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"AirPods、iPad、Apple Watch 從中國改到台灣製造","createTime":"2020-02-19T16:26:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T17:06:44.000Z","uid":104138,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"016fcc04d611ee951bd3e8172fb52af1871e463b","tid":1887642,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T16:26:23.000Z","msg":"受疫情影響，Apple 仍未能在中國回復生產力，而 Digitmes 報導指最少有部份 AirPods、iPad、Apple Watch 從中國生產改為台灣生產。而 MacBook Air、MacBook Pro 的組裝工作也已轉到台灣。<br />\n<br />\n估計，現時中國最少三分一的生產線暫停，而且二月份已沒可能回復到正常生產水平，甚至三月初能否回復正常的生產力仍存疑問。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.digitimes.com/news/a20200212PD204.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.digitimes.com%2Fnews%2Fa20200212PD204.html&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5NOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=b6b708a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.digitimes.com/news/a20200212PD204.html</a><br />\n<br />\n可以掉左部Made in China 既 iPad佢了"},{"pid":"18f809309930c03369795c6c424c144f02255490","tid":1887642,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T16:27:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eae662c64138bdb717aa99dedccb1c6e4015ab5","tid":1887642,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T16:29:27.000Z","msg":"🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼"},{"pid":"0902ce3d6ac2aed25790ce570ea26de3259c885f","tid":1887642,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T16:33:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dd601f524cc33a49b40a77308ce0c072ca5cf9f","tid":1887642,"uid":35966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T16:37:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" clas